Acknowledgements
----------------
The project started as a soft fork of cider-security-research/cicd-goat
(Cider Security, later acquired by Palo Alto Networks). The upstream's
challenge content, Docker harness, and walkthroughs have since been
removed — this repository contains only original GitHub Actions-focused
scenarios written for the scanner-comparison purpose.

We still owe a conceptual debt to the original cicd-goat for the format
of mapping deliberately-vulnerable configurations onto the OWASP Top 10
CI/CD Security Risks; if you want to learn Jenkins / GitLab / CircleCI
CI/CD attack patterns, the upstream project remains an excellent
companion:

  https://github.com/cider-security-research/cicd-goat
